name: Lessons From My Nightmares 06
description: Clip 6 of 10 in the "Lessons From My Nightmares" Collection - From an Award-Winning Short Film by Filmmaker Kira Bursky  - "Lessons From My Nightmares" is a machine learning film that follows the story of a girl dealing with insomnia due to compartmentalized thoughts and feelings. When she does sleep, she is haunted by nightmares.
